  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 179821,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ジリジリと照りつける日差しが",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The blazing sun beats down relentlessly,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179822,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "体から水分を容赦なく奪っていく。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "mercilessly stealing moisture from the body."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179823,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ひ、日差しで肌が火傷する……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"T-The sunburns my skin...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179824,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……しんどい、帰りたい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...I'm exhausted, I want to go home.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179825,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ったく、なっさけないわねぇ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Good grief, how pathetic."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179826,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　まだ砂漠の入り口だってのに」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "We're just at the entrance of the desert.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179827,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「スノーレーザー、ちょっと弱め〜、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Snow Laser, dial it down a bit—"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179828,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ひえろ〜、ひえろ〜」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Cool me down, cool me down.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179829,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「お、おお……涼しい……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"O-oh... it's cool..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179830,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いいぞ、もっとやれ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Nice, do more of that.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179831,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ケケケケケ、人間は情けねーですね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Kekekeke, humans are so weak, aren't they?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179832,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「総統、私が着いて来られるのはここまでです」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Commander, this is as far as I can follow you.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179833,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「おっ、そうか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh, I see.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179834,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「出発前にご報告を。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"A report before departure."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179835,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　二日前に出した偵察部隊の報告です」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "This is the report from the reconnaissance unit sent two days ago.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179836,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔物はやはりシャングリラに転送され、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The monsters have indeed been transported to Shangri-La,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179837,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　数が二万ほど集まると部隊として",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and when their numbers reach about twenty thousand, they organize as a unit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179838,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　各地に派遣されているそうです」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and are dispatched all across the land.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179839,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「普通、二万もの軍隊が砂漠を移動するなんて",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Normally, it would be impossible for an army of twenty thousand to traverse the desert,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179840,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　まず不可能ですが……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "but...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179841,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「何か不思議な力で砂漠に道が出来、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Apparently, by some mysterious power, a path was formed in the desert,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179842,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔軍は悠々とそこを通ったそうです」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and the demon army passed through it with ease.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179843,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふむ、そうか。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm, I see."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179844,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ケイブリスの奴は見つけたのか？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Did you find Kebris?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179845,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いえ、そこまでは……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, not that far..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179846,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ただ、兵士達がケイブリス様が来ていると",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "However, I heard the soldiers talking about Lord Kebris having come,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179847,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　話しているのを聞いたそうですので、今も",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "so I assume he is still around.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179848,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ケイブリスはシャングリラにいるか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"So Kebris is in Shangri-La.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179849,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「誰かが砂漠を横断して忍び込んでくるなど",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Since they are not expecting anyone to cross the desert and sneak in,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179850,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　想定していないからか、魔軍の警備は",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "the demon army's security is quite full of holes.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179851,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　かなり穴だらけだそうです」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179852,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「シャングリラ都市内に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It shouldn't be too difficult to sneak into the city of Shangri-La."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179853,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　忍び込むのはそれほど難しくない筈です」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179854,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「以上です。ご武運を」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That is all. Best of luck to you.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179855,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うむうむ、土産話に期待するといいぞ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Indeed, you can look forward to some souvenirs in stories.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179856,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい、ランスさんも無茶だけはしないで下さいね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, Lancer, please don’t take any reckless actions.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179857,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「って……シャングリラまで",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"But... how do we get all the way to Shangri-La?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179858,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どうやって行けばいいんだ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179859,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それはわたちが案内するでち」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I will guide you there.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179860,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、こないだの砂漠案内人……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, the desert guide from the other day...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179861,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「じゃ、ない？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Isn't it?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179862,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「違うでちよ、わたちはその人の後輩。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, I’m the junior of that person."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179863,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　名前を日立と言うでち」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "My name is Hitachi.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179864,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「先日のあの方はとても怖くて",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The person from the other day was very scary"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179865,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　シャングリラまで行けないと仰るので、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and said they couldn't go all the way to Shangri-La,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179866,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　この方を紹介して頂きました」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "so they introduced me instead.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179867,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「報酬はちゃんと貰うでちよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I will be paid properly for my services."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179868,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　危険手当で割り増しも宜しくでち」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Please include hazard pay as well.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179869,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ええ、もちろん」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, of course.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179870,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふーむ、まあちゃんと案内するなら誰でもいいか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm, well, as long as they guide us properly, anyone will do.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179871,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「では、いざ行かん！　シャングリラへ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Then, let's go! To Shangri-La!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179872,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランスが地平線の先まで広がる砂漠に向きなおる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Lance turns to face the desert stretching beyond the horizon."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179873,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「やっぱり帰ろうかな……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Maybe I should just go back...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179874,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「が、頑張りましょう……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"B-But, let's do our best...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179875,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「しかし、シャングリラってのは",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"But, what kind of place is this Shangri-La, Kaoru?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179876,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どんな場所なんだ、香ちゃん」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179877,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい、私が聞いた限りですが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well, from what I've heard,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179878,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　街が全て金-ｷﾝ-で出来ているとか……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "the entire city is made of gold..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179879,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それはもう煌びやかな光景だと」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It's said to be a dazzling sight.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179880,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ほほう、そうなのか。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh ho, is that so?"
    }
  ]
}

